OL,6,F"For the banks to pay those higher
OL,7,Finterest rates on those savings and
OL,8,Falso make a profit, they have to
OL,9,Frecover those costs somewhere and one
OL,10,Fof those ways is to pass those on to
OL,11,Fthe ordinary homeowner in Jersey who
OL,12,Fseems to be paying the price for
OL,13,Fliving in an offshore finance centre."
OL,15,FJersey homeowner Jamie Bourke says the
OL,16,Fhigh cost of getting onto the property
OL,17,Fladder is making people consider their
OL,18,Ffuture in the island.
