OL,3,CChannel Islands' mortgages cost more
OL,4,Cto benefit investors, report finds
OL,6,F"The fact that savers are now getting
OL,7,Fa bit more in their savings is a
OL,8,Fcounterbalance to the fact that
OL,9,Finterest rates have gone up and people
OL,10,Fare paying more for mortgages."
OL,12,FThe Consumer Council told me that if
OL,13,Fyou have a #100,000 mortgage then you
OL,14,Fwould be paying up to an extra #20,000
OL,15,Fmore over the lifetime of that
OL,16,Fmortgage in the Channel Islands,
OL,17,Fcompared to if you lived in the United
OL,18,FKingdom.
